<br>
Thanks for posting, it certainly makes me feel good knowing that you have an eye out for the rogue class.<br>
<br>
As I said in a previous thread, I have serious misgivings about the evade change, but it's good to see that it's being tested in &quot;real world&quot; conditions.<br>
<br>
